      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Up to 15 cm of new snow gradually fell during the working week. The snowfall was accompanied by very strong southerly winds of gale force. The wind deposited new snow on leeward places, in the gutters of northern orientations and under rock walls. Under the new snow there is a crust of older snow. In places, however, there is also square-grained snow, but this is deeper in profile."
